   <narrative xml:lang="EN">SummerProgram: Inspiring &amp; Keeping Girls In School</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Las Claras Summer Program (&quot;Veranito Las Claras&quot;) is an initiative that started on 2018 to involve young girls (7 to 14 years old) in the community of Felipillo so that they could receive several workshops and classes on vital and empowering life skills.   Furthermore, it is an initiative where our very own teen mothers at the Las Claras Program (main project) involve themselves as leaders, guiding and supervising the girls in their daily activities, in this way giving back to their community.</narrative>
  </description>
